The paper deals with shared control in complex dynamic environments, which is a topic that falls under the field of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also uses probabilistic modeling and graphical models, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses safety and efficiency, which are important considerations in control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses assistive planning, which is relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
